Name: Greater Bifra Rune
Types: Rune
Components: Bifra Rune, Level 3 Spell Slot
Description: This rune symbolizes the bridge between realms, a path from the divine to mortalkind, allowing those who channel it to tap into the power of translocation.SPACESPACEWhile wearing or using an item imbued with this rune, you gain the following feature.SPACERealm AnchorSPACEAs an action, you emit a DISTANCE10-15DISTANCE foot radius aura which warps space around you for TIME2-4TIME rounds. For the duration, you can use a bonus action on each of your turns to force a creature you can see within DISTANCE15-30DISTANCE feet of you to make a Wisdom saving throw or be teleported to a random unoccupied space within the aura. A creature may willingly fail this saving throw.SPACESPACEYou may use this rune a number of times equal to your proficiency bonus before its magic is depleted. The rune will recharge from ambient magic as you complete a long rest. This rune occupies 4 runic attunement slots.
